\n**Size**: M\n**Design Stage**: ST-3 Completed\n\n## Task Breakdown\n\n### Task 1: Verify cmd/agentd directory structure and implementation\n- [ ] Verify cmd/agentd directory exists\n- [ ] Verify main.go exists\n- [ ] Verify main.go implements controller-runtime manager initialization\n- [ ] Verify metrics-bind-address flag is defined (default: \":8080\")\n- [ ] Verify health-probe-bind-address flag is defined (default: \":8081\")\n- [ ] Verify leader-elect flag is defined (default: false)\n- [ ] Verify zap logger is initialized\n- [ ] Verify manager is created with proper options\n- [ ] Verify reconciler is registered with manager\n- [ ] Verify health checks are registered (/healthz, /readyz)","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-019/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775865103195,"end":1775865103232}}}}
