{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775865117186,"sessionID":"ses_286312c6affeHjI9ZNmHVqwJkW","part":{"id":"prt_d79cf39d5001Z0wNxN5ji8t2Dn","messageID":"msg_d79cf232e001wJAznIAdWeSYzK","sessionID":"ses_286312c6affeHjI9ZNmHVqwJkW","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-3f9b5f7e00124db9b7e0f6385cb3c692","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/design.md","limit":100},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-020: CLI pack 命令 — Design\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: The `pack` command in the AgentCube CLI is responsible for validating and preparing an agent workspace, merging CLI overrides into metadata, optionally generating a `Dockerfile`, and reporting paths to the packaged artifacts.\n6: \n7: **Module:** `cmd/cli`  \n8: **Language:** Python  \n9: **Source Root:** `/tmp/agentcube-ref/cmd/cli/`\n10: \n11: ## Architecture\n12: \n13: ### Components\n14: \n15: | Component | Location | Responsibility |\n16: |-----------|----------|----------------|\n17: | `PackRuntime` | `agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py` | Core packing logic implementation |\n18: | `MetadataService` | `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | Metadata loading, saving, and validation |\n19: | `MetadataOptions` | `agentcube/models/pack_models.py` | Dataclass for CLI option parsing |\n20: | `pack` command | `agentcube/cli/main.py` | Typer command definition and CLI entry point |\n21: \n22: ### Data Flow\n23: \n24: ```\n25: CLI Options → MetadataOptions → PackRuntime.pack()\n26:                                       ↓\n27:                      _validate_workspace_structure()\n28:                                       ↓\n29:                       _load_or_create_metadata()\n30:                                       ↓\n31:                       _apply_option_overrides()\n32:                                       ↓\n33:                     _validate_language_compatibility()\n34:                                       ↓\n35:                          _process_dependencies()\n36:                                       ↓\n37:                          _generate_dockerfile()\n38:                                       ↓\n39:                      _update_pack_metadata()\n40:                                       ↓\n41:                          _prepare_output_path()\n42:                                       ↓\n43:                             Return result\n44: ```\n45: \n46: ## Detailed Implementation\n47: \n48: ### 1. CLI Command (`agentcube/cli/main.py`)\n49: \n50: ```python\n51: def pack(\n52:     workspace: str = typer.Option(\".\", \"-f\", \"--workspace\", help=\"Path to the agent workspace directory\", show_default=True),\n53:     agent_name: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--agent-name\", help=\"Override the agent name\"),\n54:     language: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--language\", help=\"Programming language (python, java)\"),\n55:     entrypoint: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--entrypoint\", help=\"Override the entrypoint command\"),\n56:     port: Optional[int] = typer.Option(None, \"--port\", help=\"Port to expose in the Dockerfile\"),\n57:     build_mode: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--build-mode\", help=\"Build strategy: local or cloud\"),\n58:     description: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--description\", help=\"Agent description\"),\n59:     output: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--output\", help=\"Output path for packaged workspace\"),\n60:     verbose: bool = typer.Option(False, \"--verbose\", help=\"Enable detailed logging\"),\n61: ) -> None:\n62:     \"\"\"Package an agent workspace by validating structure and generating metadata.\"\"\"\n63: ```\n64: \n65: **Command behavior:**\n66: - Resolves workspace path relative to current directory if not absolute\n67: - Creates `PackRuntime` instance with verbose flag\n68: - Collects options into a dictionary\n69: - Calls `PackRuntime.pack(workspace_path, **options)`\n70: - Handles exceptions via `_handle_error(e, \"pack\", verbose)`\n71: \n72: ### 2. PackRuntime (`agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py`)\n73: \n74: #### Class Structure\n75: \n76: ```python\n77: class PackRuntime:\n78:     def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False) -> None:\n79:         self.verbose = verbose\n80:         self.logger = get_logger(__name__, level=logging.DEBUG if verbose else logging.INFO)\n81: ```\n82: \n83: #### Main Method: `pack()`\n84: \n85: ```python\n86: def pack(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n87:     \"\"\"Package an agent workspace.\n88: \n89:     Returns:\n90:         Dict containing:\n91:         - agent_name: str\n92:         - workspace_path: str (absolute path)\n93:         - metadata_path: str\n94:         - dockerfile_path: Optional[str]\n95:         - language: str\n96:         - entrypoint: str\n97:         - port: int\n98:     \"\"\"\n99:     with Progress() as progress:\n100:         task = progress.add_task(\"[cyan]Packing workspace...\", total=100)\n\n(Showing lines 1-100 of 460. Use offset=101 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-020: CLI pack 命令 — Design\n\n## Overview\n\nThe `pack` command in the AgentCube CLI is responsible for validating and preparing an agent workspace, merging CLI overrides into metadata, optionally generating a `Dockerfile`, and reporting paths to the packaged artifacts.\n\n**Module:** `cmd/cli`  \n**Language:** Python  \n**Source Root:** `/tmp/agentcube-ref/cmd/cli/`\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Components\n\n| Component | Location | Responsibility |\n|-----------|----------|----------------|\n| `PackRuntime` | `agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py` | Core packing logic implementation |\n| `MetadataService` | `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | Metadata loading, saving, and validation |\n| `MetadataOptions` | `agentcube/models/pack_models.py` | Dataclass for CLI option parsing |\n| `pack` command | `agentcube/cli/main.py` | Typer command definition and CLI entry point |","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/design.md","time":{"start":1775865117176,"end":1775865117185}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775865117200,"sessionID":"ses_286312c6affeHjI9ZNmHVqwJkW","part":{"id":"prt_d79cf3335001KEScI71jYbbgUF","messageID":"msg_d79cf232e001wJAznIAdWeSYzK","sessionID":"ses_286312c6affeHjI9ZNmHVqwJkW","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-b151155ff3c64ee4a1d60d010cf3084a","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-020/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-020/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-020: CLI pack 命令\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: 实现 AgentCube CLI 的 `pack` 命令，用于验证和准备 agent 工作区，合并 CLI 覆盖选项到元数据，可选生成 Dockerfile，并报告相关路径。这是 agent 生命周期管理的第一步，为后续的 build、publish、invoke 和 status 命令奠定基础。\n6: \n7: ## Purpose\n8: \n9: `pack` 命令是 AgentCube CLI 工具的核心命令之一，负责：\n10: \n11: 1. **工作区验证** - 确保工作区目录存在并包含必要的语言特定文件\n12: 2. **元数据管理** - 加载、验证和更新 agent 配置（`agent_metadata.yaml`）\n13: 3. **选项覆盖** - 允许通过 CLI 参数覆盖元数据中的配置项\n14: 4. **依赖处理** - 识别和处理 Python 或 Java 项目依赖\n15: 5. **Dockerfile 生成** - 根据语言和配置自动生成优化的 Dockerfile\n16: 6. **路径报告** - 输出打包后的工作区路径和元数据文件路径\n17: \n18: 该命令为开发者提供了简单、灵活的方式来准备 agent 工作区，确保其符合 AgentCube 平台的要求。\n19: \n20: ## Module\n21: \n22: `cmd/cli` - Python CLI 工具包\n23: \n24: ## Language\n25: \n26: Python 3.10+\n27: \n28: ## Size\n29: \n30: M\n31: \n32: ## Scope\n33: \n34: ### In Scope\n35: \n36: 1. **PackRuntime 类实现** (`agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py`)\n37:    - `pack()` 方法 - 主打包逻辑\n38:    - `_validate_workspace_structure()` - 工作区结构验证\n39:    - `_load_or_create_metadata()` - 元数据加载或创建\n40:    - `_apply_option_overrides()` - CLI 选项覆盖\n41:    - `_validate_language_compatibility()` - 语言兼容性验证\n42:    - `_validate_python_compatibility()` - Python 工作区验证\n43:    - `_validate_java_compatibility()` - Java 工作区验证\n44:    - `_process_dependencies()` - 依赖处理\n45:    - `_process_python_dependencies()` - Python 依赖处理\n46:    - `_process_java_dependencies()` - Java 依赖处理\n47:    - `_generate_dockerfile()` - Dockerfile 生成\n48:    - `_generate_python_dockerfile()` - Python Dockerfile 生成\n49:    - `_generate_java_dockerfile()` - Java Dockerfile 生成\n50:    - `_update_pack_metadata()` - 更新打包元数据\n51:    - `_prepare_output_path()` - 准备输出路径\n52:    - `_infer_entrypoint()` - 推断入口点命令\n53: \n54: 2. **CLI 命令定义** (`agentcube/cli/main.py`)\n55:    - `pack()` 函数 - Typer 命令定义\n56:    - 支持所有必需的 CLI 选项\n57:    - 错误处理和用户反馈\n58: \n59: 3. **元数据模型** (`agentcube/models/pack_models.py`)\n60:    - `MetadataOptions` 数据类 - CLI 选项封装\n61:    - 与 `AgentMetadata` Pydantic 模型的集成\n62: \n63: 4. **Dockerfile 模板**\n64:    - Python 基础镜像选择（python:3.10-slim）\n65:    - Java 基础镜像选择（eclipse-temurin:17-jre）\n66:    - 优化的多阶段构建\n67:    - 端口暴露和健康检查配置\n68: \n69: 5. **错误处理**\n70:    - 工作区不存在\n71:    - 缺少语言特定文件\n72:    - 无效的语言或构建模式\n73:    - 端口范围验证\n74:    - 依赖解析错误\n75: \n76: 6. **Rich 输出**\n77:    - 进度条显示打包进度\n78:    - 成功消息带路径信息\n79:    - 错误消息带详细堆栈（verbose 模式）\n80: \n81: ### Out of Scope\n82: \n83: - `build` 命令 - Docker 镜像构建\n84: - `publish` 命令 - 发布和部署\n85: - `invoke` 命令 - agent 调用\n86: - `status` 命令 - 状态查询\n87: - 自定义 Dockerfile 模板（使用标准模板）\n88: - 非 Python/Java 语言支持\n89: - 远程依赖解析和下载\n90: \n91: ## Impact Analysis\n92: \n93: ### Components Impacted\n94: \n95: 1. **CLI 工具包** (`cmd/cli`)\n96:    - 新增 `pack` 命令到 Typer 应用\n97:    - 集成 `PackRuntime` 类\n98:    - 更新错误处理逻辑\n99: \n100: 2. **运行时包** (`agentcube/runtime`)\n101:    - 新增 `pack_runtime.py` 模块\n102:    - 与其他运行时类（`BuildRuntime`、`PublishRuntime` 等）保持一致性\n103: \n104: 3. **服务包** (`agentcube/services`)\n105:    - `MetadataService` - 元数据加载和保存\n106:    - `DockerService` - Dockerfile 生成支持\n107: \n108: 4. **模型包** (`agentcube/models`)\n109:    - 新增 `pack_models.py` 模块\n110:    - `MetadataOptions` 数据类\n111: \n112: 5. **依赖管理**\n113:    - 新增 Python 依赖：`docker>=6.0.0`, `packaging>=23.0`\n114: \n115: ### Dependencies\n116: \n117: | 依赖 | 版本 | 用途 |\n118: |------|------|------|\n119: | `typer[all]` | >=0.9.0 | CLI 框架 |\n120: | `pydantic` | >=2.0.0 | 数据验证 |\n121: | `pyyaml` | >=6.0 | YAML 处理 |\n122: | `docker` | >=6.0.0 | Docker SDK（用于验证） |\n123: | `rich` | >=13.0.0 | 富文本输出 |\n124: | `packaging` | >=23.0 | 版本解析 |\n125: \n126: ### Security Considerations\n127: \n128: 1. **路径安全**\n129:    - 验证工作区路径防止路径遍历攻击\n130:    - 限制访问权限，避免敏感信息泄露\n131: \n132: 2. **元数据安全**\n133:    - 不在日志中输出敏感信息（密码、token）\n134:    - 支持环境变量覆盖敏感配置\n135: \n136: 3. **依赖安全**\n137:    - 验证依赖文件来源（requirements.txt、pom.xml）\n138:    - 不执行依赖下载（由 build 命令处理）\n139: \n140: 4. **Dockerfile 安全**\n141:    - 使用官方基础镜像\n142:    - 避免以 root 用户运行容器\n143:    - 最小化镜像层\n144: \n145: ## Design Decisions\n146: \n147: ### 语言选择\n148: \n149: **选择**: Python 3.10+\n150: \n151: **理由**:\n152: - 与现有 CLI 工具包保持一致\n153: - Typer 和 Rich 提供优秀的 CLI 开发体验\n154: - Pydantic 提供强大的数据验证\n155: - 易于维护和扩展\n156: \n157: ### 元数据文件格式\n158: \n159: **选择**: YAML 格式，主文件名为 `agent_metadata.yaml`\n160: \n161: **理由**:\n162: - 人类可读和可编辑\n163: - 支持注释\n164: - 与 Kubernetes 生态一致\n165: - 支持回退加载（`agent.yaml`、`metadata.yaml`）\n166: \n167: ### Dockerfile 生成策略\n168: \n169: **选择**: 自动生成，语言特定模板\n170: \n171: **理由**:\n172: - 减少用户手动配置\n173: - 确保最佳实践和安全配置\n174: - 支持快速迭代\n175: - 可通过 CLI 选项覆盖\n176: \n177: **Python Dockerfile 特性**:\n178: - 使用 `python:3.10-slim` 基础镜像\n179: - 多阶段构建减少镜像大小\n180: - 非 root 用户运行\n181: - 健康检查配置\n182: \n183: **Java Dockerfile 特性**:\n184: - 使用 `eclipse-temurin:17-jre` 基础镜像\n185: - 支持 JAR 文件部署\n186: - 优化的 JVM 参数\n187: - 健康检查配置\n188: \n189: ### 选项覆盖策略\n190: \n191: **选择**: CLI 选项优先级高于元数据文件\n192: \n193: **理由**:\n194: - 支持快速原型开发\n195: - 便于 CI/CD 集成\n196: - 保持元数据文件作为默认配置\n197: \n198: **优先级顺序**:\n199: 1. CLI 显式选项\n200: 2. 环境变量\n201: 3. 元数据文件值\n202: 4. 默认值\n203: \n204: ### 入口点推断策略\n205: \n206: **选择**: 智能推断，支持显式覆盖\n207: \n208: **理由**:\n209: - 减少配置负担\n210: - 支持常见项目结构\n211: - 保持灵活性\n212: \n213: **Python 推断规则**:\n214: - 检查 `main.py`、`app.py`、`server.py`\n215: - 使用 `python {file}` 作为入口点\n216: \n217: **Java 推断规则**:\n218: - 检查 `pom.xml` 中的主类\n219: - 使用 `java -jar {jar}` 作为入口点\n220: \n221: ## Alternatives Considered\n222: \n223: ### Alternative 1: 仅支持手动配置 Dockerfile\n224: \n225: **描述**: 用户必须手动提供 Dockerfile\n226: \n227: **优点**:\n228: - 完全灵活\n229: - 无需模板管理\n230: \n231: **缺点**:\n232: - 增加用户负担\n233: - 容易出现配置错误\n234: - 难以保证一致性\n235: \n236: **选择**: 不采纳 - 自动生成提供更好的用户体验\n237: \n238: ### Alternative 2: 使用 JSON 而非 YAML\n239: \n240: **描述**: 元数据文件使用 JSON 格式\n241: \n242: **优点**:\n243: - 标准格式\n244: - 广泛支持\n245: \n246: **缺点**:\n247: - 不支持注释\n248: - 可读性差\n249: - 与 Kubernetes 生态不一致\n250: \n251: **选择**: 不采纳 - YAML 更适合配置文件\n252: \n253: ### Alternative 3: 支持所有 Python 版本\n254: \n255: **描述**: 支持多个 Python 版本（3.8、3.9、3.10、3.11）\n256: \n257: **优点**:\n258: - 灵活性高\n259: - 支持旧项目\n260: \n261: **缺点**:\n262: - 增加测试负担\n263: - 维护成本高\n264: - Dockerfile 模板复杂\n265: \n266: **选择**: 不采纳 - 仅支持 Python 3.10+，保持简单\n267: \n268: ## Implementation Plan\n269: \n270: ### Phase 1: 基础结构 (Day 1)\n271: \n272: 1. 创建 `cmd/cli` 目录结构\n273: 2. 创建 `pyproject.toml` 配置文件\n274: 3. 创建 `agentcube/__init__.py`\n275: 4. 创建 `agentcube/cli/__init__.py`\n276: 5. 创建 `agentcube/cli/main.py` 框架\n277: \n278: **检查清单**:\n279: - [ ] 目录结构创建\n280: - [ ] 依赖配置\n281: - [ ] Typer 应用初始化\n282: \n283: ### Phase 2: 元数据模型 (Day 1-2)\n284: \n285: 1. 创建 `agentcube/models/__init__.py`\n286: 2. 创建 `agentcube/models/pack_models.py`\n287: 3. 实现 `MetadataOptions` 数据类\n288: 4. 创建 `agentcube/models/metadata.py`（如果不存在）\n289: 5. 实现 `AgentMetadata` Pydantic 模型\n290: \n291: **检查清单**:\n292: - [ ] `MetadataOptions` 实现\n293: - [ ] `AgentMetadata` 实现\n294: - [ ] 验证器实现\n295: - [ ] 单元测试\n296: \n297: ### Phase 3: 元数据服务 (Day 2)\n298: \n299: 1. 创建 `agentcube/services/__init__.py`\n300: 2. 创建 `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`\n301: 3. 实现 `MetadataService` 类\n302: 4. 实现加载、保存、更新方法\n303: 5. 实现工作区验证方法\n304: \n305: **检查清单**:\n306: - [ ] `MetadataService` 实现\n307: - [ ] 文件加载逻辑\n308: - [ ] 文件保存逻辑\n309: - [ ] 验证逻辑\n310: - [ ] 单元测试\n311: \n312: ### Phase 4: PackRuntime 实现 (Day 2-4)\n313: \n314: 1. 创建 `agentcube/runtime/__init__.py`\n315: 2. 创建 `agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py`\n316: 3. 实现 `PackRuntime` 类\n317: 4. 实现所有私有方法\n318: \n319: **关键方法**:\n320: ```python\n321: class PackRuntime:\n322:     def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False) -> None:\n323:         self.verbose = verbose\n324:         self.logger = get_logger(__name__)\n325: \n326:     def pack(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n327:         \"\"\"主打包方法\"\"\"\n328:         pass\n329: \n330:     def _validate_workspace_structure(self, workspace_path: Path) -> None:\n331:         \"\"\"验证工作区结构\"\"\"\n332:         pass\n333: \n334:     def _load_or_create_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> AgentMetadata:\n335:         \"\"\"加载或创建元数据\"\"\"\n336:         pass\n337: \n338:     def _apply_option_overrides(self, metadata: AgentMetadata, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> AgentMetadata:\n339:         \"\"\"应用选项覆盖\"\"\"\n340:         pass\n341: \n342:     def _validate_language_compatibility(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> None:\n343:         \"\"\"验证语言兼容性\"\"\"\n344:         pass\n345: \n346:     def _generate_dockerfile(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> Optional[Path]:\n347:         \"\"\"生成 Dockerfile\"\"\"\n348:         pass\n349: ```\n350: \n351: **检查清单**:\n352: - [ ] `PackRuntime` 类实现\n353: - [ ] 工作区验证\n354: - [ ] 元数据处理\n355: - [ ] 依赖处理\n356: - [ ] Dockerfile 生成\n357: - [ ] 单元测试\n358: \n359: ### Phase 5: CLI 命令集成 (Day 4)\n360: \n361: 1. 在 `agentcube/cli/main.py` 中实现 `pack()` 命令\n362: 2. 定义所有 CLI 选项\n363: 3. 实现 Rich 进度显示\n364: 4. 实现错误处理\n365: \n366: **命令签名**:\n367: ```python\n368: def pack(\n369:     workspace: str = typer.Option(\".\", \"-f\", \"--workspace\", help=\"Path to the agent workspace directory\", show_default=True),\n370:     agent_name: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--agent-name\", help=\"Override the agent name\"),\n371:     language: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--language\", help=\"Programming language (python, java)\"),\n372:     entrypoint: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--entrypoint\", help=\"Override the entrypoint command\"),\n373:     port: Optional[int] = typer.Option(None, \"--port\", help=\"Port to expose in the Dockerfile\"),\n374:     build_mode: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--build-mode\", help=\"Build strategy: local or cloud\"),\n375:     description: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--description\", help=\"Agent description\"),\n376:     output: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--output\", help=\"Output path for packaged workspace\"),\n377:     verbose: bool = typer.Option(False, \"--verbose\", help=\"Enable detailed logging\"),\n378: ) -> None:\n379:     \"\"\"Pack an agent workspace for deployment.\"\"\"\n380:     pass\n381: ```\n382: \n383: **检查清单**:\n384: - [ ] CLI 命令实现\n385: - [ ] 选项定义\n386: - [ ] Rich 输出\n387: - [ ] 错误处理\n388: - [ ] 集成测试\n389: \n390: ### Phase 6: Dockerfile 模板 (Day 5)\n391: \n392: 1. 创建 Dockerfile 模板\n393: 2. 实现 Python Dockerfile 生成\n394: 3. 实现 Java Dockerfile 生成\n395: 4. 优化镜像大小\n396: \n397: **Python Dockerfile 模板**:\n398: ```dockerfile\n399: FROM python:3.10-slim as builder\n400: \n401: WORKDIR /app\n402: COPY requirements.txt .\n403: RUN pip install --user --no-cache-dir -r requirements.txt\n404: \n405: FROM python:3.10-slim\n406: \n407: WORKDIR /app\n408: COPY --from=builder /root/.local /root/.local\n409: COPY . .\n410: \n411: ENV PATH=/root/.local/bin:$PATH\n412: \n413: EXPOSE {port}\n414: \n415: HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=10s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \\\n416:   CMD curl -f http://localhost:{port}/health || exit 1\n417: \n418: CMD {entrypoint}\n419: ```\n420: \n421: **检查清单**:\n422: - [ ] Python Dockerfile 模板\n423: - [ ] Java Dockerfile 模板\n424: - [ ] 优化和测试\n425: \n426: ### Phase 7: 测试 (Day 5-6)\n427: \n428: 1. 单元测试\n429: 2. 集成测试\n430: 3. 端到端测试\n431: \n432: **单元测试覆盖**:\n433: - `PackRuntime` 所有方法\n434: - `MetadataService` 所有方法\n435: - `MetadataOptions` 验证\n436: - 错误处理\n437: \n438: **集成测试**:\n439: - Python 工作区打包\n440: - Java 工作区打包\n441: - 选项覆盖\n442: - Dockerfile 生成\n443: \n444: **端到端测试**:\n445: - 完整打包流程\n446: - 输出验证\n447: - 元数据验证\n448: \n449: **检查清单**:\n450: - [ ] 单元测试\n451: - [ ] 集成测试\n452: - [ ] 端到端测试\n453: - [ ] 覆盖率 > 80%\n454: \n455: ### Phase 8: 文档 (Day 6-7)\n456: \n457: 1. 添加 docstrings\n458: 2. 创建示例\n459: 3. 更新 README\n460: 4. 添加使用指南\n461: \n462: **文档内容**:\n463: - API 文档\n464: - 使用示例\n465: - 命令参考\n466: - 最佳实践\n467: \n468: **检查清单**:\n469: - [ ] API 文档\n470: - [ ] 使用示例\n471: - [ ] README 更新\n472: - [ ] 使用指南\n473: \n474: ## Testing Strategy\n475: \n476: ### Unit Tests\n477: \n478: 1. **PackRuntime 测试**\n479:    - 工作区验证\n480:    - 元数据加载和创建\n481:    - 选项覆盖\n482:    - 语言兼容性验证\n483:    - 依赖处理\n484:    - Dockerfile 生成\n485: \n486: 2. **MetadataService 测试**\n487:    - 文件加载（包括回退逻辑）\n488:    - 文件保存\n489:    - 元数据更新\n490:    - 工作区验证\n491: \n492: 3. **MetadataOptions 测试**\n493:    - `from_options` 方法\n494:    - 字段验证\n495:    - 默认值\n496: \n497: 4. **CLI 命令测试**\n498:    - 参数解析\n499:    - 错误处理\n500:    - 输出格式\n501: \n502: ### Integration Tests\n503: \n504: 1. **Python 项目打包**\n505:    - 简单 Python 项目\n506:    - 带依赖的 Python 项目\n507:    - 多文件 Python 项目\n508: \n509: 2. **Java 项目打包**\n510:    - 简单 Java 项目\n511:    - 带 Maven 依赖的项目\n512: \n513: 3. **选项覆盖**\n514:    - 所有 CLI 选项\n515:    - 组合选项\n516:    - 无效选项\n517: \n518: 4. **Dockerfile 生成**\n519:    - Python Dockerfile\n520:    - Java Dockerfile\n521:    - 自定义端口和入口点\n522: \n523: ### End-to-End Tests\n524: \n525: 1. **完整打包流程**\n526:    - 创建工作区\n527:    - 运行 pack 命令\n528:    - 验证输出\n529:    - 验证元数据\n530:    - 验证 Dockerfile\n531: \n532: 2. **错误场景**\n533:    - 工作区不存在\n534:    - 缺少 Python 文件\n535:    - 缺少 pom.xml\n536:    - 无效端口\n537:    - 无效语言\n538: \n539: ### Test Coverage\n540: \n541: 目标: > 80% 代码覆盖率\n542: \n543: ## Configuration\n544: \n545: ### CLI 选项\n546: \n547: | 选项 | 短选项 | 类型 | 默认值 | 说明 |\n548: |------|--------|------|--------|------|\n549: | `--workspace` | `-f` | str | `\".\"` | 工作区目录路径 |\n550: | `--agent-name` | - | Optional[str] | `None` | 覆盖 agent 名称 |\n551: | `--language` | - | Optional[str] | `None` | 编程语言（python, java） |\n552: | `--entrypoint` | - | Optional[str] | `None` | 覆盖入口点命令 |\n553: | `--port` | - | Optional[int] | `None` | Dockerfile 中暴露的端口 |\n554: | `--build-mode` | - | Optional[str] | `None` | 构建策略（local, cloud） |\n555: | `--description` | - | Optional[str] | `None` | Agent 描述 |\n556: | `--output` | - | Optional[str] | `None` | 打包工作区输出路径 |\n557: | `--verbose` | - | bool | `False` | 启用详细日志 |\n558: \n559: ### 元数据字段\n560: \n561: | 字段 | 类型 | 默认值 | 说明 |\n562: |------|------|--------|------|\n563: | `agent_name` | str | (required) | Agent 唯一名称 |\n564: | `description` | Optional[str] | `None` | 人类可读的摘要 |\n565: | `language` | str | `\"python\"` | 编程语言 |\n566: | `entrypoint` | str | (required) | 启动 agent 的命令 |\n567: | `port` | int | `8080` | agent runtime 暴露的端口 |\n568: | `build_mode` | str | `\"local\"` | 构建策略（local, cloud） |\n569: | `region` | Optional[str] | `None` | 部署区域 |\n570: | `version` | Optional[str] | `None` | 发布的语义版本字符串 |\n571: | `requirements_file` | Optional[str] | `\"requirements.txt\"` | Python 依赖文件 |\n572: \n573: ### 环境变量\n574: \n575: | 环境变量 | 说明 |\n576: |---------|------|\n577: | `AGENTCUBE_VERBOSE` | 启用详细日志 |\n578: | `AGENTCUBE_DEFAULT_LANGUAGE` | 默认语言 |\n579: | `AGENTCUBE_DEFAULT_PORT` | 默认端口 |\n580: \n581: ## API Specification\n582: \n583: ### CLI 命令\n584: \n585: ```bash\n586: kubectl-agentcube pack [OPTIONS]\n587: ```\n588: \n589: ### 输出格式\n590: \n591: **成功输出**:\n592: ```\n593: ✓ Successfully packed agent\n594: \n595: Agent Name: my-agent\n596: Workspace: /path/to/workspace\n597: Metadata: /path/to/workspace/agent_metadata.yaml\n598: Dockerfile: /path/to/workspace/Dockerfile\n599: ```\n600: \n601: **错误输出**:\n602: ```\n603: ✗ Error packaging agent: Workspace does not exist: /invalid/path\n604: ```\n605: \n606: **详细错误输出** (verbose 模式):\n607: ```\n608: ✗ Error packaging agent: Workspace does not exist: /invalid/path\n609: \n610: Traceback (most recent call last):\n611:   File \"/path/to/main.py\", line 42, in pack\n612:     result = runtime.pack(workspace_path, **options)\n613:   ...\n614: ValueError: Workspace does not exist: /invalid/path\n615: ```\n616: \n617: ### 元数据文件格式\n618: \n619: ```yaml\n620: agent_name: my-agent\n621: description: A sample agent\n622: language: python\n623: entrypoint: python main.py\n624: port: 8080\n625: build_mode: local\n626: region: us-west-1\n627: version: 1.0.0\n628: requirements_file: requirements.txt\n629: ```\n630: \n631: ## Security Considerations\n632: \n633: 1. **路径验证**\n634:    - 验证工作区路径在当前目录或子目录\n635:    - 防止路径遍历攻击\n636:    - 限制符号链接跟随\n637: \n638: 2. **文件权限**\n639:    - 验证文件可读性\n640:    - 验证目录可写性（用于输出）\n641:    - 不处理敏感文件（如 `.ssh`、`.aws`）\n642: \n643: 3. **元数据安全**\n644:    - 不在日志中输出敏感信息\n645:    - 支持环境变量覆盖\n646:    - 验证端口范围（1-65535）\n647: \n648: 4. **依赖安全**\n649:    - 仅读取依赖文件，不执行\n650:    - 不验证依赖完整性（由 build 命令处理）\n651:    - 警告使用不安全的依赖\n652: \n653: 5. **Dockerfile 安全**\n654:    - 使用官方基础镜像\n655:    - 非 root 用户运行\n656:    - 最小化镜像层\n657:    - 健康检查配置\n658: \n659: ## Performance Considerations\n660: \n661: 1. **文件 I/O**\n662:    - 最小化文件系统访问\n663:    - 使用缓存避免重复读取\n664:    - 并行处理多个文件（如果适用）\n665: \n666: 2. **内存使用**\n667:    - 流式处理大文件\n668:    - 避免不必要的数据复制\n669:    - 使用生成器而非列表\n670: \n671: 3. **启动时间**\n672:    - 延迟加载非核心模块\n673:    - 优化导入\n674:    - 减少初始化开销\n675: \n676: 4. **并发处理**\n677:    - 异步文件 I/O（如果适用）\n678:    - 并行验证多个文件\n679: \n680: ## Monitoring and Metrics\n681: \n682: ### 日志\n683: \n684: 使用 Python 标准日志模块：\n685: \n686: ```python\n687: import logging\n688: \n689: logger = logging.getLogger(__name__)\n690: ```\n691: \n692: **日志级别**:\n693: - `DEBUG`: 详细调试信息\n694: - `INFO`: 一般信息（进度、成功消息）\n695: - `WARNING`: 警告信息\n696: - `ERROR`: 错误信息\n697: - `CRITICAL`: 严重错误\n698: \n699: ### 进度显示\n700: \n701: 使用 Rich `Progress` 组件：\n702: \n703: ```python\n704: from rich.progress import Progress, SpinnerColumn\n705: \n706: with Progress(\n707:     SpinnerColumn(),\n708:     *Progress.get_default_columns(),\n709: ) as progress:\n710:     task = progress.add_task(\"[green]Packing agent...\", total=100)\n711:     # 更新进度\n712: ```\n713: \n714: ### 错误追踪\n715: \n716: - 使用 Python 标准异常\n717: - 提供详细的错误消息\n718: - 支持 verbose 模式的完整堆栈\n719: \n720: ## Open Questions\n721: \n722: 1. **Q1**: 是否需要支持更多编程语言？\n723:    - **当前**: 仅支持 Python 和 Java\n724:    - **讨论**: Go、Node.js 等语言需求\n725:    - **决策**: 初始仅支持 Python 和 Java，后续根据需求添加\n726: \n727: 2. **Q2**: 是否需要支持自定义 Dockerfile 模板？\n728:    - **当前**: 使用内置模板\n729:    - **讨论**: 用户可能需要自定义模板\n730:    - **决策**: 初始不支持，后续根据需求添加\n731: \n732: 3. **Q3**: 是否需要支持依赖自动下载？\n733:    - **当前**: 仅验证依赖文件\n734:    - **讨论**: 自动下载可提高用户体验\n735:    - **决策**: 不支持，由 build 命令处理\n736: \n737: 4. **Q4**: 是否需要支持工作区模板？\n738:    - **当前**: 用户手动创建工作区\n739:    - **讨论**: 预定义模板可简化初始化\n740:    - **决策**: 考虑添加 `init` 命令\n741: \n742: ## Next Steps\n743: \n744: 1. 实现 Phase 1-2（基础结构和元数据模型）\n745: 2. 实现 Phase 3（元数据服务）\n746: 3. 实现 Phase 4（PackRuntime）\n747: 4. 实现 Phase 5（CLI 命令集成）\n748: 5. 实现 Phase 6（Dockerfile 模板）\n749: 6. 实现 Phase 7（测试）\n750: 7. 实现 Phase 8（文档）\n751: 8. 集成到 CI/CD 流程\n752: \n753: ## References\n754: \n755: - [AgentCube CLI Spec](../cli-toolkit/spec.md)\n756: - [AgentCube CLI Design](../cli-toolkit/design.md)\n757: - [Typer Documentation](https://typer.tiangolo.com/)\n758: - [Pydantic Documentation](https://docs.pydantic.dev/)\n759: - [Rich Documentation](https://rich.readthedocs.io/)\n760: - [Docker Best Practices](https://docs.docker.com/develop/dev-best-practices/)\n761: - [Python Packaging Guide](https://packaging.python.org/)\n762: - [Maven Documentation](https://maven.apache.org/guides/)\n\n(End of file - total 762 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-020: CLI pack 命令\n\n## Overview\n\n实现 AgentCube CLI 的 `pack` 命令，用于验证和准备 agent 工作区，合并 CLI 覆盖选项到元数据，可选生成 Dockerfile，并报告相关路径。这是 agent 生命周期管理的第一步，为后续的 build、publish、invoke 和 status 命令奠定基础。\n\n## Purpose\n\n`pack` 命令是 AgentCube CLI 工具的核心命令之一，负责：\n\n1. **工作区验证** - 确保工作区目录存在并包含必要的语言特定文件\n2. **元数据管理** - 加载、验证和更新 agent 配置（`agent_metadata.yaml`）\n3. **选项覆盖** - 允许通过 CLI 参数覆盖元数据中的配置项\n4. **依赖处理** - 识别和处理 Python 或 Java 项目依赖\n5. **Dockerfile 生成** - 根据语言和配置自动生成优化的 Dockerfile\n6. **路径报告** - 输出打包后的工作区路径和元数据文件路径\n\n该命令为开发者提供了简单、灵活的方式来准备 agent 工作区，确保其符合 AgentCube 平台的要求。\n\n## Module","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-020/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775865117169,"end":1775865117198}}}}
